L5->L6: 2.0

# Smoothing multiplier is
# `(size(Lbottom)/size(Lbase))^(Lbottom-Lbase) = (30/1)^(1/(6-4)) = 30^(1/2)`
#
# size(L4) = size(Lbase) = 1
# size(L5) = size(L4) * 30^(1/2) ~= 5
# size(L6) = size(L5) * 30^(1/2) = 30

init 1
5: 2
6: 30
